data.description: Welcome home! This stunning 2 story has been tastefully updated. Features include luxury vinyl plank on the first floor and finished basement. The modern kitchen offers wood cabinets, granite counters, tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances and a counter bar this kitchen a fabulous gathering space! Finished basement adds nearly 1000 sqft of finished living space! Coming Soon! Showings start 02/08/2024.
